Course, when I got up
this morning, I like to die.

232
00:21:37,342 --> 00:21:40,028
Once I started movin' around,
I felt pretty good.

233
00:21:41,302 --> 00:21:44,173
- You walked all of that way
across town? - Yes, ma'am.

234
00:21:44,208 --> 00:21:48,255
- Ooh, that's a long walk, woman.
- Yes, indeedy.

235
00:21:50,766 --> 00:21:53,817
You know, you come into town
and go to one of the mass meetings.

236
00:21:53,852 --> 00:21:55,953
You feel like you could
walk forever too.

237
00:21:55,988 --> 00:21:58,961
Mmm, I gots me a ride to work,
and I sleep through it most of the time.

238
00:21:58,996 --> 00:22:00,848
I don't need no inspiration.

239
00:22:17,084 --> 00:22:18,590
Odessa.

240
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:25,197
Now, I hear that gettin' up early,
movin' around,

241
00:22:25,232 --> 00:22:27,576
does a soul good
in the mornin'.

242
00:22:28,903 --> 00:22:31,814
I just wonder what it does
for 'em in the afternoon.

243
00:22:34,597 --> 00:22:39,667
